FV is a great server.  Very little no drop items, TLC, great people (in general, even those that don't roleplay and will let you know it) and a low population make for a very good server.  I was talking to Syll the other day, and one of the first things I said when he asked how I liked being back was that the people here are great.  Sure, you get your closeminded idiots, your d00ds, your trainers and your KS'ers, but in the end most of the people here are pretty cool.  Tzaroth's a great guy, he helped me out, RP'ed with me, and helped reinforce how fantastic this server is.  I disagree with him bothering to flame someone in this case, but I still like him.  Bald's a guildleader in my guild, and I agree with a lot of what he says, but I understand that not everyone will.  You can disagree with someone and still get along.  Don't burn your bridges because of one disagreement. <br>
